In [Spring 3.2 reference docs][1], section 17.3.3, Supported method argument types:

&gt;The following are the supported method arguments:
&gt;
&gt; - Request or response objects (Servlet API). Choose any specific request or response type, for example ServletRequest or HttpServletRequest.&lt;br&gt;
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&gt;
